node.text:
Have you ever thought about mobile home investing as something that can generate passive income? No! It’s ok we didn’t either at first. 
.
.
We looked over them for years because when everyone thinks about real estate, they think about SFH, multi-family, duplex’s etc.  Mobile Homes were last on that list.
.
.
Until we decided to tap into this untapped market and start investing.  When we first started we didn’t know anyone that looked like us doing mobile home investing.  After we start flipping consistently, Byron said “let’s teach this” we have too! This has changed our lives….

📌 we both were able to not go back to work and focus on investing full time 

📌 we were able to start investing with minimum capital 

📌credit was not a factor on us getting started 
.
.
We knew holding this information in would not be of justice to us, yes we would be well off financially but it’s a different feeling when you know you have changed 1000s of lives by pouring this sector into the masses. 
.
.
These daily testimonials is our “WHY” in this! It sparks a different type of fire in us to keep going, keep providing knowledge and keep giving you the tools to successfully make this not just a hobby but an actual business. 
.
.
S/O our superstar student Brandy, who killed her 1st mobile home deal! 🎉🎉 she’s looking at $40k over time and got $15k as her down payment getting right back what she put into it!!! #theMHEIway
.
.
Are you ready to join the family? Come join us in Chicago 09/19 for our MHEI presents “mix & motivate” conference.  You don’t want to miss this highly anticipated event.  We will be going over Wholesaling, Moving, Buy & Hold, Fix & Flipping and much more.  CLICK LINK IN THE BIO TO PURCHASE YOUR TICKET NOW!

node.text:
Don’t let great opportunities pass you by‼️

As you drive for dollars through mobile home park communities, many times you see empty lots aka empty pads. 

You normally continue driving looking for vacant or mobile homes with for sale signs. Right?

I’m here to tell you, don’t overlook those lots anymore‼️

How many times have you come across “mobile home needs to be moved” while searching online for mobile homes? 🤔

Well, @byronssellers tells you in many of our @instagram Lives, this is the place to shop those mobile homes needing to be moved; Mobile home parks. 

Here are a few tips:

📌 Call mobile home parks and ask are they looking for #mobilehomes to be moved in their community

📌 Reach out to local #mobilehomemovers to get quotes on the potential move.

📌 Go see the mobile home and make sure it’s no structural damage, which could inhibit the move. 

Empty Mobile Home Lots = #opportunity 

Always ask yourself, “How can I help a family get affordable housing & be rewarded financially for my service?”

Lead with value and create opportunities for other to people to win. That is a formula for #success 

Let’s get it Family!
